Wang Youqi, chief technology 
officer of Yashentech Corp., talks about his efforts to use 
coal to reduce black-carbon soot emissions from diesel engines 
in  China .   China's use of coal and its effects on the environment is 
a featured story in the May issue of Bloomberg Markets 
magazine. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 02:25
 